<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.9.10">
<l>niṉṟuniṉ ṟupala nāḷuykku mivvuṭa ṉīṅkippōy</l>
<l>ceṉṟuceṉ ṟākiluṅ kaṇṭucaṉ maṅkaḻip pāṉeṇṇi</l>
<l>yoṉṟiyoṉ ṟiyula kampaṭait tāṉkavi yāyiṉēṟ</l>
<l>keṉṟumeṉ ṟumiṉi maṟṟoru varkavi yēṟkumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Counting, although going on, going [and] going, on leaving this body</l>
<l>that is sent lasting, lasting for many days, seeing [and] discarding birth,</l>
<l>for me who is a poet of the one who created the world, being all one [with it],</l>
<l>is a poem on any other suitable, now and forever and ever?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
